description.narrative: Information Redacted Information Redacted[Covers individual experts and consultants possessing special, current knowledge, and skill which may be combined with extensive operational experience. They provide information, opinions, advice, or recommendations that enhance understanding of complex issues or improve the quality and timeliness of policy development and decision-making. Contract experts and consultants do not supervise or perform operating functions nor do they receive direct supervision. Contract experts and consultants serving on advisory committees are to be assigned to subobject code 2505.]. Information has been redacted in accordance with the two principled exceptions defined in the Foreign Aid Transparency and Accountability Act (FATAA) of 2016: the health and security of implementing partners, and the national interest of the United States.. ADMINISTRATIVE MANAGEMENT[Covers individual experts and consultants possessing special, current knowledge, and skill which may be combined with extensive operational experience. They provide information, opinions, advice, or recommendations that enhance understanding of complex issues or improve the quality and timeliness of policy development and decision-making. Contract experts and consultants do not supervise or perform operating functions nor do they receive direct supervision. Contract experts and consultants serving on advisory committees are to be assigned to subobject code 2505.]. This modification hereby; De-obligates Option Year 3 funds from CLIN 301/3003/3004.
